com.mesosphere.sdk.offer.evaluate.placement

Class AgentRule

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mesosphere.sdk.offer.evaluate.placement.AgentRule
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    PlacementRule

    public class AgentRule
extends java.lang.Object
implements PlacementRule
    This rule enforces that a task be placed on a provided agent ID, or enforces that the task avoid that agent ID, depending on the factory method used.
